      "text": "World League Soccer, known as Pro Soccer (Japanese: プロサッカー, Hepburn: Puro sakkā) in Japan, is an association football-based sports video game developed by C-Lab, and released for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System and X68000 in 1991.",
